r bellies are scorched by hunger, they are turned back to the Fire and given drink from a boiling spring ['ayn aniyah] whose heat has reached its peak and whose blaze has intensified.\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"5":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.55","c":"تُسْقَى","d":"ٰàَqْsُt","e":"ٰàَqْsُt"},{"b":"0.82","h":"2.02","c":"مِنْ","d":"ْnِm","e":"ْnِm"},{"b":"1.1","h":"2.51","c":"عَيْنٍ","d":"ٍnْyَʿع","e":"ٍnْyَʿع"},{"b":"2.1","h":"4.11","c":"ءَانِيَةٍ","d":"ٍẗَyِnāَء","e":"ٍẗَyِnāَء"}],"a":{"g":"They will be given drink from a boiling spring."}},"6":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.75","c":"لَيْسَ","d":"َsْyَّl","e":"َsْyَّl"},{"b":"0.62","h":"1.65","c":"لَهُمْ","d":"ْmُhَl","e":"ْmُhَl"},{"b":"1.1","h":"2.63","c":"طَعَامٌ","d":"ٌmāَʿعَṭ","e":"ٌmāَʿعَṭ"},{"b":"2.2","h":"4.56","c":"إِلَّا","d":"āَّlِiʾ","e":"āَّlِiʾ"},{"b":"3.1","h":"6.27","c":"مِنْ","d":"nِm","e":"nِm"},{"b":"4.4","h":"7.29","c":"ضَرِيعٍ","d":"ٍʿعyِrَḍ","e":"ٍʿعyِrَḍ"}],"a":{"g":"For them there will be no food except from a poisonous, thorny plant"}},"7":{"w":[{"b":"0.04","h":"0.3","c":"لَا","d":"āَّl","e":"āَّl"},{"b":"0.37","h":"1.03","c":"يُسْمِنُ","d":"ُnِmْsُy","e":"ُnِmْsُy"},{"b":"1.2","h":"2.47","c":"وَلَا","d":"āَlَw","e":"āَlَw"},{"b":"1.7","h":"3.56","c":"يُغْنِي","d":"àِnْغُy","e":"àِnْغُy"},{"b":"2.7","h":"5.3","c":"مِنْ","d":"nِm","e":"nِm"},{"b":"3.8","h":"6.41","c":"جُوعٍ","d":"ٍʿعwُjg","e":"ٍʿعwُjg"}],"a":{"g":"Which neither nourishes nor avails against hunger."}},"8":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.25","c":"وُجُوهٌ","d":"ٌhwُjgُw","e":"ٌhwُjgُw"},{"b":"1.9","h":"2.51","c":"يَوْمَئِذٍ","d":"ٍhdِyʾَmْwَy","e":"ٍhdِyʾَmْwَy"},{"b":"3.7","h":"4.27","c":"نَاعِمَةٌ","d":"ٌẗَmِʿعāَّn","e":"ٌẗَmِʿعāَّn"}],"a":{"g":"[Other] faces, that Day, will show pleasure."}},"9":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.8","c":"لِسَعْيِهَا","d":"āَhِyْʿعَsِّl","e":"āَhِyْʿعَsِّl"},{"b":"1.2","h":"2.87","c":"رَاضِيَةٌ","d":"ٌẗَyِḍāَr","e":"ٌẗَyِḍāَr"}],"a":{"g":"With their effort [they are] satisfied"}},"10":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.4","c":"فِي","d":"àِf","e":"àِf"},{"b":"0.36","h":"1.06","c":"جَنَّةٍ","d":"ٍẗَّnَjg","e":"ٍẗَّnَjg"},{"b":"2.1","h":"3.31","c":"عَالِيَةٍ","d":"ٍẗَyِlāَʿع","e":"ٍẗَyِlāَʿع"}],"a":{"g":"In an elevated garden,"}},"11":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.65","c":"لَا","d":"āَّl","e":"āَّl"},{"b":"0.39","h":"1.37","c":"تَسْمَعُ","d":"ُʿعَmْsَt","e":"ُʿعَmْsَt"},{"b":"1.2","h":"2.88","c":"فِيهَا","d":"āَhyِf","e":"āَhyِf"},{"b":"2.2","h":"5.62","c":"لَاغِيَةً","d":"ًẗَyِغَٰl","e":"ًẗَyِغَٰl"}],"a":{"g":"Wherein they will hear no unsuitable speech."}},"12":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.65","c":"فِيهَا","d":"āَhyِf","e":"āَhyِf"},{"b":"0.74","h":"2.01","c":"عَيْنٌ","d":"ٌnْyَʿع","e":"ٌnْyَʿع"},{"b":"2.4","h":"4.13","c":"جَارِيَةٌ","d":"ٌẗَyِrāَjg","e":"ٌẗَyِrāَjg"}],"a":{"g":"Within it is a flowing spring."}},"13":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.75","c":"فِيهَا","d":"āَhyِf","e":"āَhyِf"},{"b":"0.85","h":"2.22","c":"سُرُرٌ","d":"ٌrُrُs","e":"ٌrُrُs"},{"b":"2.6","h":"4.19","c":"مَرْفُوعَةٌ","d":"ٌẗَʿعwُfْrَّm","e":"ٌẗَʿعwُfْrَّm"}],"a":{"g":"Within it are couches raised high"}},"14":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.42","c":"وَأَكْوَابٌ","d":"ٌbāَwْkَaʾَw","e":"ٌbāَwْkَaʾَw"},{"b":"2.3","h":"2.84","c":"مَوْضُوعَةٌ","d":"ٌẗَʿعwُḍْwَّm","e":"ٌẗَʿعwُḍْwَّm"}],"a":{"g":"And cups put in place","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                ثم يطأطىء رأسه فإذا أزواجه ﴿ وأكواب موضوعة ونمارق مصفوفة وزرابى مبثوثة ﴾ {} ثم اتكأ فقال: ﴿ الحمد لله الذي هدانا لهذا وما كنا لنهتدى لو لا أن هدانا الله ﴾ {} ثم ينادى مناد تحيون فلا تموتون أبدا وتقيمون فلا تظعنون أبدا وتصحون فلا تمرضون أبدا\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                Then he lowers his head, and behold, his spouses, **and cups placed, and cushions arrayed, and carpets spread out.** Then he reclines and says: **\"Praise be to Allah, Who has guided us to this. And we would never have been guided if Allah had not guided us.\"** Then a caller calls out: \"You live, so you never die; and you abide, so you never depart; and you are healthy, so you never fall ill.\"\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"15":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.36","c":"وَنَمَارِقُ","d":"ُqِrāَmَnَw","e":"ُqِrāَmَnَw"},{"b":"1.3","h":"2.53","c":"مَصْفُوفَةٌ","d":"ٌẗَfwُfْṣَm","e":"ٌẗَfwُfْṣَm"}],"a":{"g":"And cushions lined up"}},"16":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.45","c":"وَزَرَابِيُّ","d":"ُّàِbāَrَzَw","e":"ُّàِbāَrَzَw"},{"b":"1.5","h":"3.2","c":"مَبْثُوثَةٌ","d":"ٌẗَhtwُhtْbَm","e":"ٌẗَhtwُhtْbَm"}],"a":{"g":"And carpets spread around."}},"17":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.75","c":"أَفَلَا","d":"āَlَfَaʾ","e":"āَlَfَaʾ"},{"b":"0.8","h":"2.08","c":"يَنْظُرُونَ","d":"َnwُrُẓnَy","e":"َnwُrُẓnَy"},{"b":"2.7","h":"4.64","c":"إِلَى","d":"àَlِiʾ","e":"àَlِiʾ"},{"b":"3.0","h":"5.36","c":"الْإِبِلِ","d":"ِlِbِiʾْlٱ","e":"ِlِbِiʾْlٱ"},{"b":"3.9","h":"6.84","c":"كَيْفَ","d":"َfْyَk","e":"َfْyَk"},{"b":"4.5","h":"8.03","c":"خُلِقَتْ","d":"ْtَqِlُhk","e":"ْtَqِlُhk"}],"a":{"g":"Then do they not look at the camels - how they are created?"}},"18":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"1.2","c":"وَإِلَى","d":"àَlِiʾَw","e":"àَlِiʾَw"},{"b":"0.55","h":"2.1","c":"السَّمَاءِ","d":"ِءٓāَmَّslٱ","e":"ِءٓāَmَّslٱ"},{"b":"3.1","h":"4.82","c":"كَيْفَ","d":"َfْyَk","e":"َfْyَk"},{"b":"3.7","h":"5.94","c":"رُفِعَتْ","d":"ْtَʿعِfُr","e":"ْtَʿعِfُr"}],"a":{"g":"And at the sky - how it is raised?"}},"19":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.48","c":"وَإِلَى","d":"àَlِiʾَw","e":"àَlِiʾَw"},{"b":"0.56","h":"1.37","c":"الْجِبَالِ","d":"ِlāَbِjgْlٱ","e":"ِlāَbِjgْlٱ"},{"b":"1.6","h":"3.26","c":"كَيْفَ","d":"َfْyَk","e":"َfْyَk"},{"b":"2.3","h":"4.42","c"