":"ْmُhَbāَyِiʾ"}],"a":{"g":"Indeed, to Us is their return."}},"26":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.04","c":"ثُمَّ","d":"َّmُht","e":"َّmُht"},{"b":"1.3","h":"1.5","c":"إِنَّ","d":"َّnِiʾ","e":"َّnِiʾ"},{"b":"2.7","h":"2.74","c":"عَلَيْنَا","d":"āَnْyَlَʿع","e":"āَnْyَlَʿع"},{"b":"3.9","h":"4.77","c":"حِسَابَهُمْ","d":"mُhَbāَsِḥ","e":"mُhَbāَsِḥ"}],"a":{"g":"Then indeed, upon Us is their account."}}}